These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Game   | scrabble | snooker | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, lilac
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Color   | lavender | ebony | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, engineer, designer
1. the social-worker is on the far left##1
2. the designer is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Job   | social-worker | engineer | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
